                         ~{=======================}~
                           \     Welcome to:     /
                            )    HZmoria 0.1    (
                           /   by Ben Shadwick   \
                         ~{=======================}~

This is a fork of the classic roguelike UMoria, version 5.6. It is dedicated
to the many contributors to and fans of the original game over its multiple
decades of life, and is my own attempt to keep interest going in the game so
that it may continue to inspire more successors.

HZMoria is free software. It comes with ABSOLUTELY NO WARRANTY, and you are
welcome to distribute it under certain conditions; for details, type
control-V after starting a character or read the accompanying documentation.

Please visit https://github.com/HunterZ/hzmoria for support and releases.
